# Installation

## Database
First you need to create a MySQL database. The application will connect through PDO.
### config/database.php
```php
<?php

/*
 * config/database.php
 */

$server     = 'localhost';
$username   = 'db_username';
$password   = 'db_pass';
$database   = 'fletnix_db';

try{
    $connection = new PDO("mysql:host=$server;dbname=$database;", $username, $password);
} catch(PDOException $e) {
    die ( "Connection failed!" . $e->getMessage());
}
```
